7.2 Internal Functions
======================

 -- Function: instapapier-add-url url

     Internal function to add a URL to Instapaper.  This is the core
     function that handles authentication, API communication, and error
     handling.

     *Arguments:*
     URL
          The URL string to add to Instapaper.

     *Returns:* The response buffer on success, or ‘nil’ on error.

     *HTTP Status Codes:*
     ‘201’
          Successfully added URL
     ‘400’
          Bad request (invalid URL format)
     ‘403’
          Authentication failed

     This function is not interactive and is meant to be called by other
     Instapapier commands.


